{"context":"To be honest, I did not expect that.","lemma":"to be honest","senses":[{"emojiDescription":["\uD83D\uDDE3\uFE0F"],"index":1,"phrasemeKind":"DiscourseFormula","unitKind":"Phrasem"},{"emojiDescription":["\uD83E\uDD1D"],"index":2,"phrasemeKind":"Collocation","unitKind":"Phrasem"}]}
